pull.title: [Qt] Add upload and download info to the peerlist (debug menu)
pull.body:
Makes the peer list display how much you've uploaded/downloaded from each peer. 

Here's a [screenshot](https://i.imgur.com/MhPbItp.png) of how it looks. You can now sort to see who are the peers you've uploaded the most too.

I also moved `RPCConsole::FormatBytes` to `guiutil::formatBytes` so I could use it in the peerlist
